        "text": "## Stability-Constant Measurements at 25 °C\n\n**85.0%** of all stability-constant measurements in the NIST SRD-46 database were conducted at 25 °C.\n\n| Condition | Count | Percentage |\n|-----------|------:|----------:|\n| At 25 °C | 67,237 | 85.04% |\n| Other temperatures | 11,826 | 14.96% |\n| **Total** | **79,063** | **100%** |",
